{"tid":1132521,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜 汶 澤 仍 欠 程 美 段 和 網 友 們 一 個 道 歉 ！","createTime":"2019-04-30T11:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:09:19.000Z","uid":95418,"like":117,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0cd2dad339804c9e7eefcb1380e09c15d50203","tid":1132521,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:01:30.000Z","msg":"程美段被拖糧一事終於已發展到尾聲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖則杜汶澤擁有的公司因拖糧一事已發聲明公開向程美段道歉，但卻沒有因在社交媒體上以個人名義抹黑及侮辱程美段而作出道歉。更猖狂的是杜汶澤除了在自己專頁上發表了威風八面的言論，還侮辱所有反對佢的人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪證1 杜汶澤抹黑程美段</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oC69fvp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoC69fvp.png&h=a90ec3f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rD3C8Qq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrD3C8Qq.png&h=0cfcadfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">罪證2 公開侮辱所有反對杜汶澤嘅網民</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pq5erDZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpq5erDZ.png&h=bd03394c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1MhprQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1MhprQ.png&h=23f389ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">講事講理都要比佢話係假波毒撚，社記深黃，垃圾藍屍。我夠話你係霸道硬頸垃圾廢佬添</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你作為一個公眾人物，所有對外嘅言論都要負上責任。郁啲就公審人，擺起個款就以為自己啱，真係知道做錯時又擺兄弟上枱。處事方法十足十啲𡃁仔咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請杜汶澤先生為自已所發表嘅言論負責，並向所有受你發言而影響到嘅人作出道歉！</span><br />\n</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59b711590f5a13eacdcceb7e79cbff29bc96462","tid":1132521,"uid":95418,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:09:22.000Z","msg":"睇到佢撐豪仔篇已真係睇火爆，咁利用朋友都得。豪仔重同佢做Frd真係要小心啲，話唔定有一日杜汶澤賣得佢重勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc191f7ebaed860cbaf9a4346db82fd82c77e2e5","tid":1132521,"uid":95418,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b59b711590f5a13eacdcceb7e79cbff29bc96462","tid":1132521,"uid":95418,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:09:22.000Z","msg":"睇到佢撐豪仔篇已真係睇火爆，咁利用朋友都得。豪仔重同佢做Frd真係要小心啲，話唔定有一日杜汶澤賣得佢重勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:11:29.000Z","msg":"借豪仔想拎光環，係真兄弟嘅話唔洗周街唱你地關係係點嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3efa009efb0756539ee8b49b943dfcc778e50a","tid":1132521,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"仲撐杜汶澤嘅人，仲有咩理據"},{"pid":"546308dd5813fe057d9aecf6ded9ac0ef3036283","tid":1132521,"uid":95418,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"2a3efa009efb0756539ee8b49b943dfcc778e50a","tid":1132521,"uid":12628,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:11:34.000Z","msg":"仲撐杜汶澤嘅人，仲有咩理據"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:19:09.000Z","msg":"不外乎假波，整容，中共陰謀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d13fb7fdcaeec29cc2c21e4713f3e2b285cb6e64","tid":1132521,"uid":95418,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-30T11:27:37.000Z",